  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Tax avoidance - don't get caught out
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Personal stories from people who have been caught up in tax avoidance schemes.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
